<title>laminas-mail</title>
<indexterm><primary>laminas-mail</primary></indexterm>

<para><anchor xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2laminas_2laminas-mail_2_r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md6283"/> <link xlink:href="https://github.com/laminas/laminas-mail/actions?query=workflow%3A"></link></para>

<para><computeroutput>Laminas\Mail</computeroutput> provides generalized functionality to compose and send both text and MIME-compliant multipart email messages. Mail can be sent with <computeroutput>Laminas\Mail</computeroutput> via the <computeroutput>Mail\Transport\Sendmail</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Mail\Transport\Smtp</computeroutput> or the <computeroutput>Mail\Transport\File</computeroutput> transport. Of course, you can also implement your own transport by implementing the <computeroutput>Mail\Transport\TransportInterface</computeroutput>.</para>

